author: Matt Dathan
title: PM REJECTS petition to cancel Trump's state visit to UK | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Theresa May REJECTS petition signed by 1.8m people demanding she cancels Trump's state visit to the UK In response today the Government insists Trump should be extended 'full courtesy' of a state visit to Britain later this year In a statement the Government said it 'recognises the strong views expressed by the many signatories of the petition' But says it doesn't support the motion to bar Trump from the UK and state visit will go ahead as planned
